/**
 * Returns a stream of ProductRelationSnapshot objects filtered by the specified relation type.
 * <p>
 * This method provides special handling for MODIFICATION relation type, where it also includes
 * CORRECTION relations as part of the result. This special case exists for backward compatibility
 * with legacy code that treats corrections similarly to modifications.
 * <p>
 * For all other relation types, this method returns only relations that exactly match the
 * specified type.
 *
 * @param relationType the type of relation to filter by
 * @return a stream of ProductRelationSnapshot objects that match the specified relation type,
 *         with special handling for MODIFICATION to include CORRECTION relations
 */
